## Queue.resume() method

Resumes the processing of this queue globally.

The method reverses the pause operation by resuming the processing of the queue.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
resume(): Promise<void>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

Promise&lt;void&gt;
